title: Looking for duo partner ( support pref )
body:
I've recently been demoted from silver 3 to silver 5 and my mmr is lower than it should be and I'm being paired with bronze. I have started maining adc again and am looking for a player with good game knowledge that wants to duo with me. Preferably non-toxic please.

Thanks in advance :)

replies.body: Dude, i play a mean sup if you want to duo? IGN - Mullyplant94
